attributes.name: DOMINANCE
attributes.definition: solves challenges, drives action and results, and moves at a fast pace.

attributes.name: INFLUENCE
attributes.definition: gains energy from people, is enthusiastic, and prefers group participation.

attributes.name: STEADINESS
attributes.definition: is loyal, listens well, employs specialized skills, and uses a calm approach.

attributes.name: COMPLIANCE
attributes.definition: follows roles, focuses on details, thinks analytically, acts diplomatically.
